#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.nanmax.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.nanmax"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:1 of
msgid ""
"Return the maximum of an array or maximum along an axis, ignoring any "
"NaNs.  When all-NaN slices are encountered a ``RuntimeWarning`` is raised"
" and NaN is returned for that slice."
msgstr ""
"返回数组的最大值或沿轴的最大值，忽略任何 NaN。当遇到全为 NaN 的切片时，会"
"引发 ``RuntimeWarning`` 并返回 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:5 of
msgid ""
"Tensor containing numbers whose maximum is desired. If `a` is not a "
"tensor, a conversion is attempted."
msgstr "包含所需最大值的 Tensor。如果 `a` 不是 Tensor，则尝试进行转换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:8 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which the maximum is computed. The default is to compute the "
"maximum of the flattened tensor."
msgstr "计算最大值的轴。默认计算展平后 Tensor 的最大值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:11 of
msgid ""
"Alternate output array in which to place the result.  The default is "
"``None``; if provided, it must have the same shape as the expected "
"output, but the type will be cast if necessary.  See `doc.ufuncs` for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"用于放置结果的替代输出数组。默认为 ``None``；如果提供，其形状必须与预期"
"输出相同，但必要时会进行类型转换。详见 `doc.ufuncs`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:16 of
msgid ""
"If this is set to True, the axes which are reduced are left in the result"
" as dimensions with size one. With this option, the result will broadcast"
" correctly against the original `a`.  If the value is anything but the "
"default, then `keepdims` will be passed through to the `max` method of "
"sub-classes of `Tensor`.  If the sub-classes methods does not implement "
"`keepdims` any exceptions will be raised."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为 True，则在结果中保留被规约的轴，其大小为 1。使用此选项时，结果"
"可以正确地与原始 `a` 广播。如果该值不是默认值，则 `keepdims` 会被传递给 `"
"Tensor` 子类的 `max` 方法。如果子类方法未实现 `keepdims`，则会引发异常。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:16 of
msgid ""
"If this is set to True, the axes which are reduced are left in the result"
" as dimensions with size one. With this option, the result will broadcast"
" correctly against the original `a`."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为 True，则被约简的轴将在结果中保留为大小为一的维度。使用此选项时"
"，结果将能够正确地与原始 `a` 进行广播。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:20 of
msgid ""
"If the value is anything but the default, then `keepdims` will be passed "
"through to the `max` method of sub-classes of `Tensor`.  If the sub-"
"classes methods does not implement `keepdims` any exceptions will be "
"raised."
msgstr ""
"如果值不是默认值，则 `keepdims` 将传递给 `Tensor` 子类的 `max` 方法。如果"
"子类方法未实现 `keepdims`，则会引发异常。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:26 of
msgid ""
"**nanmax** -- A tensor with the same shape as `a`, with the specified "
"axis removed. If `a` is a 0-d tensor, or if axis is None, a Tensor scalar"
" is returned.  The same dtype as `a` is returned."
msgstr ""
"**nanmax** -- 一个与 `a` 形状相同的 Tensor，指定轴被移除。如果 `a` 是 0 "
"维 Tensor，或 axis 为 None，则返回一个 Tensor 标量。返回的数据类型与 `a` "
"相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`nanmin`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:34 of
msgid "The minimum value of a tensor along a given axis, ignoring any NaNs."
msgstr "沿给定轴的 Tensor 最小值，忽略任何 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:36 of
msgid ":py:obj:`amax`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:37 of
msgid "The maximum value of a tensor along a given axis, propagating any NaNs."
msgstr "沿给定轴的 Tensor 最大值，传播任何 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:39 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fmax`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:40 of
msgid "Element-wise maximum of two tensors, ignoring any NaNs."
msgstr "两个 Tensor 的逐元素最大值，忽略任何 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:42 of
msgid ":py:obj:`maximum`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:43 of
msgid "Element-wise maximum of two tensors, propagating any NaNs."
msgstr "两个 Tensor 的逐元素最大值，传播任何 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:45 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isnan`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:46 of
msgid "Shows which elements are Not a Number (NaN)."
msgstr "显示哪些元素是 Not a Number (NaN)。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:48 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isfinite`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:49 of
msgid "Shows which elements are neither NaN nor infinity."
msgstr "显示哪些元素既不是 NaN 也不是无穷大。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:51 of
msgid ":py:obj:`amin`, :py:obj:`fmin`, :py:obj:`minimum`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:54 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:55 of
msgid ""
"MaxFrame uses the IEEE Standard for Binary Floating-Point for Arithmetic "
"(IEEE 754). This means that Not a Number is not equivalent to infinity. "
"Positive infinity is treated as a very large number and negative infinity"
" is treated as a very small (i.e. negative) number."
msgstr ""
"MaxFrame 使用 IEEE 二进制浮点数算术标准 (IEEE 754)。这意味着 Not a Number"
" 不等同于无穷大。正无穷被视为一个非常大的数，负无穷被视为一个非常小（即"
"负数）的数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmax.nanmax:60 of
msgid "If the input has a integer type the function is equivalent to np.max."
msgstr "如果输入是整数类型，则此函数等效于 np.max。"

